11)the CGSO to prepare the RSMIs for all issuances of inventory, a copy of which shall be furnished to the City Accountant for recording; and
12)the Inventory Committee to conduct physical count of balances of inventories at year end, pursuant to COA Circular No. 2015-009, and the relevant provisions of the Manual on the NGAS for LGUs and IPSAS No. 12

