We recommended, in accordance with COA Circular No. 2012-001 dated June 14, 2012 and Section 17 of Rule VI of the RIRR of RA No. 9184, that the City require:
(1) The City Accountant, to submit to the Audit Team, supporting documents, together with the disbursement voucher, for all contracts for infrastructure after payment has been made; 
(2) The Bids and Awards Committee, to submit to the Audit Team, a copy of the contract with the supporting documents within five days from perfection thereof to facilitate the legal, auditorial and technical review.
